sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend (Browser / Ajax)
    participant API as Backend REST API
    participant SS as Product Search Service
    participant DB as Database

    U->>FE: Type keyword in search bar

    FE->>API: GET /api/products?keyword=iphone&page=0&size=12

    API->>SS: searchProducts(keyword,page,size)

    SS->>DB: SELECT * FROM PRODUCTS\nWHERE product_name LIKE keyword%\nLIMIT page,size
    DB-->>SS: product list

    SS->>DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM PRODUCTS\nWHERE product_name LIKE keyword%
    DB-->>SS: totalElements

    SS-->>API: ProductPage

    API-->>FE: ApiResponse<ProductPage>

    FE-->>U: Update product grid dynamically